<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The count() method, defined by the Countable interface, uses $this-&gt;_count, which is set in the constructor of Zend_Config. The problem now is, when you unset a value (done via the magic method __unset()), $this-&gt;_count is not decreased by one. So when you count() the Zend_Config object after you unset a node, you get the wrong number.</p>

    </div>
